title: Thief 2 The Metal Age [English] [PC]
description:
Thief II: The Metal Age is a stealth-based game, sequel to Thief: The Dark Project
The basic gameplay is similar to the original Thief, with a few new elements, including technological gadgets such as a remote eye camera and more intelligent level designs. Other changes include an increase in the number of A.I. behaviors, and the addition of female guards and soldiers.
